#Lyrics
In peace I will lie down and sleep; for you alone, O LORD, make me dwell in safety. (Psalm 4:8)  [Responsory] Into your hands, O Lord, I commend my spirit. You have redeemed me, O Lord, faithful God. Into your hands, O Lord, I commend my spirit.  The LORD Almighty bless and keep us; the LORD make His face shine upon us and be gracious unto us; the LORD lift up His countenance upon us and give us peace. Amen. (Numbers 6:24-26)

